		<div class="entry-meta">
			<span class="entry-date"><a href="http://blog.cedricbonhomme.org/2011/06/20/une-nouvelle-version-de-pyaggr3g470r-pointe-son-nez/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2011-06-20T23:00:37+00:00">June 20, 2011</time></a></span> <span class="byline"><span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://blog.cedricbonhomme.org/author/cedric/" rel="author">Cédric</a></span></span>		</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
